Hey, my fellow Canadians! I've some news for you:

* Added tracking: Wish Post, LWE (Logistics Worldwide Express), TEA Post, GLS, SDA Express Courier, Polar Express, Hermes, PanAsia, DHL Netherlands
* Yearly subscription!
* Updated tracking number detection: DHL eCommerce, DHL Express, Correos Spain, Parcelforce, Royal Mail, TNT, Bpost, Australia Post, DPD, UBI Smart Parcel, Sky56, Flyt, SFC, CDEK, Aliexpress Standard Shipping, Fedex, TNT.
* Detect 20 digit numbers as PostNord for Denmark, Deutsche Post for Germany and FedEx for the rest
* Use your device country to select which tracker to choose if there are multiple options for the same tracking number.
* Track shipments from Estonia to Ukraine with Meest Express
* Detect Joom order ids and suggest using tracking number instead
* Track 16-digit numbers with Canada Post, DHL, Hermes, Australia Post
* Australia Post: Detect eParcel numbers like 3690308546
* UTEC: Fix tracking with updated web site

Fixed bugs:
* Parcelforce some times returns empty status, app will not show it now
* Some of you enter tracking numbers with spaces, and tracking didn’t work that way, app will remove spaces from now on

Tell me (request@parcelsapp.com) what postal and courier services you are missing and I will add them in next release!

P.S. Please write a review about the app in the App Store, it will help me add all the necessary delivery services, translate all statuses from Chinese to English, and make the app you’ll love!
